60
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:27,160
Aren't you Mr. Leng
from the Leng family?

61
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,600
I'm Song Ruoyun from the Song family.

62
00:03:28,920 --> 00:03:30,120
