everyone who is going to leave.

87
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,560
- Yes.
- Yes.

88
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,440
Miss Song

89
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,280
is...

90
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,360
Mr. Leng.

91
