No.

95
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:51,160
I'm not saying you don't like women.

96
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:51,840
It's just I've never seen

97
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:53,320
any woman around you.

98
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,160
There hasn't been any man, of course.

99
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,480
You can tell me now.

100
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,480
What I said is

101
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,840
helping me to get rid of Song Ruoyun.

102
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:06,480
That means

103
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,920
you have to take me out of the hotel.

104
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,920
I think Miss Song has people
blocking the gate of the hotel.

105
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:10,920
Do you need me

106
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,960
to get you waitress' clothes?

107
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:12,440
No.

108
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,880
Get me a dress.

109
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:15,440
Shouldn't you sneak out?

110
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,440
The more high-profile,

111
00:05:17,440 --> 00:05:19,160
