It's noisy here.

124
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,800
Let's hurry home.

125
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,200
We shall go separate ways.

126
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,720
I'll meet you at the intersection ahead.

127
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:33,360
Why hasn't Miss Luo come yet?

128
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,080
It's hard to get lost here.

129
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,440
She won't come.

130
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,080
Didn't she say she would meet us
at the intersection?

131
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,360
That's interesting.

132
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,160
Kevin.

133
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,000
Let's go.

134
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,880
I know you too well.

135
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,400
