152
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:33,840
Didn't you get a text today

153
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,040
which asked you to go to the hotel?

154
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,600
I was worried you would be in trouble.

155
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,960
That's why I was waiting for you
at the door.

156
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,240
Why are you

157
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,240
acting so strange today?

158
