159
00:07:43,960 --> 00:07:46,040
(There is a bug in the comic book world)

160
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,480
(and I'm playing the wrong role.)

161
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:49,960
(I also have a consciousness.)

162
